(1) npx create-react-app ./my-clone (No capital letter)

(2) delete all src, then create src again

(3) Delete all comments in index.html

(4) Install nmo install react-icons   This is the only installation according to the mentor

(5) Add VSCode extention  ES7 React/Redux/GraphQL/React-Native snippet
    A. Select the Extension Icon, Search for es7 snippets
    B. Then download then install ES7 React/Redux/GraphQL/React-Native snippet
    C. Now my VSCode can have the following feature, by typing rafce, to genereate a compoment template
       rafce:  React Arrow Function Export Component 

(6) Type rafce to create an App component templete

(7) git init and commit first commit.